test_even_range:
assert [0, 1, 2] == [4]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 4
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [4]
  + [0, 1, 2]
test_large_range:
assert [0, 1, 2] == [2]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 2
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [2]
  + [0, 1, 2]
